			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Citrix Engineer</p>
<p>
We are a vibrant and dynamic IT cloud service provider looking for an enterprise level Citrix guru. &nbsp;Our diverse base of SME customers, located across the USA and Canada, is growing rapidly which means we need to fill this critical role immediately!</p>
<p>
Our company prides itself on being a leading provider of on-demand virtual application delivery. We now have offices on both the East and West Coast.</p>
<p>
Our mission is to provide the best service in the industry. Our environment is informal but our people are passionate. They are innovative and solution oriented. We value relationships and actions are rewarded. We like to throw some fun into the mix too!</p>
<p>
Our Ideal Citrix Guru/Engineer:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Excellent problem solving skills supporting End Users in a multi platform environment ensuring 99.99% SLA (Service Level Agreement) is maintained.</li>
<li>
Strong work ethic with excellent people skills</li>
<li>
Excellent communications skills with the ability to communicate complex technical terms in simple layman&#39;s language</li>
<li>
Proven ability to complete tasks on time and within a timely manner and to exceed all customer expectations</li>
</ul>
<p>
Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>
IT Infrastructure and Development Support</li>
<li>
Desktop Engineering Support</li>
<li>
Remote Administration (Citrix XenAPP, RSA, VPN, RDP)</li>
<li>
Hardware/Software Deployment &amp; Configuration Development and Support</li>
<li>
Technical, Logistic &amp; Customer Support</li>
</ul>
<p>
Our Technical Environment:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Hardware: HP Blade Servers / HP SAN</li>
<li>
Operating Systems: Windows 2008 R2 64 bit</li>
<li>
Mail Clients: Outlook 2003, 2007, 2010 w/ Exchange 2000, 2007, 2010</li>
<li>
Virtualization: Citrix XenServer 5.6</li>
<li>
Application Suites: Should be flexible to work with many different applications</li>
<li>
Networking: LAN/WAN, DHCP, DNS, FTP, VPN, SSH, TCP/IP, RDP</li>
<li>
Other: Active Directory, Wireless Technology, Antivirus Solutions.</li>
</ul>
<p>
This job is in our San Francisco, CA office and not a remote position</p>
<p>
Are you looking for an opportunity to show off your skills? If you are, please respond with a cover letter and resume.</p>
